            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and cook for 3 min until the tomatoes have reduced a little</p>\n<p>Tip: the sugar helps balance the acidity of the tomatoes</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>Knorr</strong></span> <strong>chicken stock</strong> <strong>cube</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"><strong>[s]</strong></span> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 5,
